3515d554-c64e-4e58-9550-91cbf387976f	b9e48d84-9081-4267-acd8-32a3d5cbe2cf	1	                                |\n| `matric-fleet`       | Fleet management                              | –                                          |\n\n## Platform Packages (`@matric/*`)\n\n- `@matric/core` – Workflow engine and state machine  \n- `@matric/cms` – Content management and versioning  \n- `@matric/runtime` – Execution environments  \n- `@matric/api` – API gateway and GraphQL endpoints  \n- `@matric/types` – Shared TypeScript types  \n- `@matric/common` – Shared utilities  \n\n## Core Services (Docker)\n\n| Service     | Port(s) | Purpose                           |\n|-------------|---------|-----------------------------------|\n| PostgreSQL  | 5432    | Primary relational database       |\n| MongoDB     | 27017   | Document store (authenticated)   |\n| Redis       | 6379    | Caching and session store         |\n| Hasura      | 8080    | GraphQL engine                    |\n| Keycloak    | 8081/8443 | OIDC authentication              |\n| Vault       | 8200    | Secrets management                |\n| MailPit     | 1025/8025 | Email testing                    |\n| Grafana     | 3000    | Monitoring dashboards             |\n| Prometheus  | 9090    | Metrics collection                |\n\n## `matric-memory` Architecture (Rust)\n\nThe memory system is a Rust library composed of the following crates:\n\n- `matric-core` – Core traits, types, error handling  \n- `matric-db` – PostgreSQL + pgvector data layer  \n- `matric-search` – Hybrid search (FTS + semantic + RRF fusion)  \n- `matric-inference`	[-0.028238539,0.034570362,-0.15738073,-0.071187645,0.10021157,-0.08656518,0.016970027,0.0074564735,-0.032118917,-0.026935441,0.04321221,-0.015979787,0.094096124,-0.004529722,0.019378725,-0.022379138,-0.039828494,0.0007555144,-0.024408424,0.014375236,0.010728216,-0.046351064,-0.03088236,0.004347536,0.09915969,0.06230286,0.018554343,-0.0025388198,-0.0002759099,-0.020718327,0.06489317,0.005