542b6211-17dc-4184-b4f9-931d852c5a8e	2628f641-8423-4a05-93c6-b3f5fbfbc1db	0	# Matric‑Memory Architecture & Model Configuration\n\n> A Rust‑based, AI‑enhanced note storage system that combines **semantic search**, **NLP pipelines**, and a **job‑queue** for background processing.\n\n> **Core idea** – Keep the data immutable and store only the current working version, enriched by an LLM. Use a hybrid search engine (FTS + vector similarity) to surface relevant notes quickly.\n\n---\n\n## 1. Workspace Layout\n\n```\nmatric-memory (workspace)\n├─ matric-core          # Core traits, types, error handling\n├─ matric-db            # PostgreSQL + pgvector layer\n├─ matric-search        # Hybrid search engine (FTS + semantic)\n├─ matric-inference     # LLM/Ollama abstraction\n├─ matric-jobs          # Background job queue & worker\n└─ matric-api           # HTTP REST API (Axum)\n```\n\n> *See ADR‑02: “Multi‑crate workspace” – promotes modularity and independent compilation.*\n\n---\n\n## 2. System Architecture Diagram\n\n```\nHotM Frontend\n	[-0.012386485,0.062973276,-0.1679975,-0.03980465,0.02219581,-0.07689991,0.01762049,0.0052134683,-0.0463576,-0.019573176,0.030112006,0.03877053,0.07925328,0.011315068,-0.033026546,0.020579878,-0.025822347,-0.0046355817,-0.033063162,0.019946365,-0.0049555968,-0.0022743356,-0.030299416,-0.022099255,0.064008415,0.059765782,-0.019371131,-0.036671564,-0.0005415039,0.0334092,0.053471826,-0.005992781,-0.020295769,0.0041034245,-0.053628374,-0.053369936,0.021721227,-0.0045160674,-0.021003854,0.036474653,0.00337053,0.006501562,-0.007970884,-0.07251751,0.052281365,0.03452493,0.062049445,-0.034921065,0.08823113,-0.09483751,0.0012530118,-0.001810755,0.04395147,0.0201195,0.06341837,0.020208512,0.051544428,-0.034013275,0.03308772,-0.028343596,0.058316708,0.08103682,-0.04450034,0.12023118,0.009175048,-0.002617369,0.012409855,0.030252716,-0.012605085,-0.047475748,0.05747759,0.0061322576,0.010900568,0.04494042,-0.001289087,0.012610452,-0.03135902,-0.00140754