8b5c564d-10f1-49b7-9b87-5d98675dbabb	2628f641-8423-4a05-93c6-b3f5fbfbc1db	5	> *See ADR‑05: “Priority‑based job queue” – ensures critical tasks finish first.*\n\n---\n\n## 6. Hybrid Search Engine\n\n| Mode | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| **FTS Only** | PostgreSQL `tsvector` + GIN index |\n| **Semantic Only** | Cosine similarity over `pgvector` |\n| **Hybrid** (default) | Combines both with **Reciprocal Rank Fusion (RRF)** |\n\n### RRF Formula\n\n```\nscore(doc) = Σ 1 / (k + rank_i(doc))\n```\n\n- `k` = 60 (smoothing factor)  \n- `rank_i(doc)` = rank from each component (FTS, semantic)\n\n> *RRF is a proven, language‑agnostic fusion strategy that balances recall and precision.*\n\n### Search Process\n\n1. Execute FTS if weight > 0.  \n2. Execute semantic query if weight > 0.  \n3. Fuse with RRF.  \n4. Apply filters (archived, tags, collection).  \n5. Return top‑k snippets.\n\n---\n\n## 7. Database Schema Overview\n\n| Table | Purpose | Key Indexes |\n|-------|---------|-------------|\n| `note` | Metadata (id, timestamps, flags) | — |\n	[0.005699377,0.010762075,-0.20042403,-0.03911944,0.06993215,-0.055829626,0.04640435,0.011088488,-0.020243935,0.0090463245,-0.02126337,0.034384612,0.059114944,0.0066430923,0.007911209,-0.029867114,0.015093117,-0.03988378,-0.019679332,0.038742434,0.0024861312,0.03177741,-0.032591704,-0.058349986,0.01717615,0.065240495,-0.0276057,-0.019012861,-0.008067292,0.008436557,0.041097097,0.01291227,-0.03241875,-0.040151067,-0.04118849,-0.02897931,0.014553768,-0.018187819,0.018405475,0.010769532,0.010863649,0.023598488,0.052799042,-0.07788678,0.016805429,0.00606932,0.0336908,0.035489712,0.07531851,-0.11184422,-0.03422044,0.036884222,-0.0065588257,-0.03140983,0.039846823,0.084428035,-0.015687075,0.0471316,0.02373021,-0.014163639,0.07770857,0.019614449,-0.05573714,0.03686399,-0.012975466,-0.004732148,0.021051822,0.09153872,-0.01907317,-0.011687137,0.0004387542,-0.0064927605,0.0064342683,0.0472672,-0.024498915,0.030996583,0.0024133297,-0.023