9e9e8e7f-35fe-40af-b61b-f6ecec4d504e	4072e1b1-7f5f-4346-b7ea-b4f818cd61db	0	# Matric‑CLI Evaluation / Testing System Architecture\n\nMatric‑CLI is a TypeScript/Node.js AI‑powered CLI assistant that comes with a **robust, multi‑dimensional evaluation framework**.  \nThe framework lives under `/evals` (core code) and `/source/eval` (scoring logic & benchmarks).  \nBelow is a fully‑detailed, context‑rich description of the architecture, components, and usage.\n\n---\n\n## 1. Evaluation / Testing System Architecture\n\n### 1.1 Core Components\n\n| Directory / File | Purpose |\n|------------------|---------|\n| `/evals/cli.ts` | Entry point for all CLI‑driven evaluations |\n| `/evals/lib/types.ts` | Fundamental type definitions (`EvalConfig`, `Scenario`, `Result`, etc.) |\n| `/evals/lib/scenarioLoader.ts` | Parses YAML/JSON scenario files |\n| `/evals/lib/fixtureManager.ts` | Handles temporary project scaffolds (empty, template, git‑clone) |\n| `/evals/lib/evalRunner.ts` | Orchestrates scenario execution (voting, retries, parallelism) |\n	[0.017002508,0.02348237,-0.16918182,-0.07246148,0.06542566,-0.053075086,0.03411885,0.024128156,-0.005121356,0.0011065156,-0.0055083535,0.028432567,0.08922572,0.02245376,0.0052162088,-0.04727262,0.0069356263,-0.016739763,-0.0041037425,-0.0037584442,0.022361798,-0.03342879,-0.015908329,-0.020451197,0.09324841,0.08040754,-0.017576652,0.034103222,-0.05232994,0.00975232,-0.016287476,-0.0078572985,-0.02471424,-0.01729762,-0.047762766,-0.033807896,0.059719335,-0.0019968308,-0.026774652,-0.042650536,-0.042656027,0.04230009,0.026931671,-0.018793283,0.05044564,0.014207535,0.028955255,0.012506755,0.058183923,-0.07480086,-0.06322706,0.015475007,0.03351525,-0.012836183,0.07949747,0.035187617,-0.04150821,0.03474481,-0.02343759,-0.033266366,0.078956336,0.05020595,-0.02637093,0.09116783,0.04528991,-0.023351833,-0.031215612,0.02825812,0.018468283,-0.050062723,0.018678533,0.0050890977,-0.044443723,0.0073397853,-0.03839785,0.001208261,-0.029808113,-0.0202