3d5ba745-5e10-49a4-a45e-6af25ff0a8a2	26d57c87-5712-47fb-95fc-80b61c04f061	4	The Blind Spot Detector aligns with **cognitive ergonomics** and **knowledge management theory**. By formalizing the act of *searching for absence*, it mirrors human creative processes: noticing voids, hypothesizing missing links, and then constructing new content. It also dovetails with continuous learning pipelines, ensuring that a knowledge base evolves dynamically rather than stagnating.\n\n---\n\n### Next Steps\n\n1. Prototype embedding pipeline and density analysis.  \n2. Integrate Wikidata categories as a baseline ontology.  \n3. Build UI components for gap notification and Auto‑Research.  \n4. Conduct user trials to refine thresholds and prompts.  \n\n---\n	[0.007272484,0.02708936,-0.17189077,-0.07384124,0.08715926,0.045413166,0.06225729,-0.006287617,0.01052824,-0.026664581,0.012232975,-0.0063307234,0.08441715,0.067281,0.02925157,0.0023456162,-0.033646286,-0.029981362,-0.039199416,0.012039664,-0.03225475,0.007961132,0.010560622,-0.023414275,0.031831123,0.04980981,-0.0009954276,0.009189306,0.0047528893,0.00023561147,0.049570326,-0.02433184,-0.010789619,-0.017345104,-0.053067736,-0.03698452,0.090884894,0.03590162,-0.022083506,0.026327236,0.021914884,-0.0023240375,0.005502539,-0.019028338,0.009036592,0.007310463,0.029852826,-3.163251e-05,0.051839672,-0.06620214,-0.0045824726,0.00518975,0.006550604,0.0036665087,0.07850639,0.03239632,0.021302165,-0.022978505,0.024512377,-0.040831998,0.089318626,0.07448027,-0.0059111393,0.08039215,0.041109536,-0.017124081,-0.05452867,0.06077698,-0.018104015,-0.041388713,0.019881034,-0.00075144175,-0.0139689185,0.092728734,-0.04460296,0.039987307,-0.004557392,0.0020948926,-0.036381807,0.037390802,0.02479247,0.02665445,0.075625345,0.020553,0.1017072,-0.033101186,-0.0342603,-0.05356737,0.0016692848,0.08854796,-0.032622498,0.008492499,0.011797751,0.006553584,-0.03373099,-0.0034808503,0.009909312,0.0011912431,-0.055087868,-0.012159498,-0.059830923,-0.038707882,