5de16789-0240-496c-a5ca-32bc3e79d4dd	1c77dc3b-b229-4bb8-97e2-c2d90385e4a0	1	| **Performance** | Less noise means faster query times and clearer results. |\n\n---\n\n## 3. Implementation Details\n\n```text\nrelevance_score = base_score × exp(-λ × days_since_access)\n```\n\n- **`base_score`** – Initial relevance (e.g., based on creation date, semantic similarity, or popularity).\n- **`λ`** – Decay rate; tuned per domain or user preferences.\n- **`days_since_access`** – Time elapsed since last interaction.\n\n> **Twist** – *Backlinks slow decay*:  \n> `relevance_score = base_score × exp(-λ × days_since_access) × (1 + α × backlinks)`\n> \n> Here, `α` boosts the score proportionally to the number of backlinks, keeping widely referenced knowledge prominent.\n\n---\n\n## 4. Contextual Connections\n\n### 4.1 Matric‑Memory Architecture & Model Configuration\n- **Rust‑based AI‑enhanced storage**: The Matric platform already leverages semantic search and NLP pipelines.  \n	[0.04364598,0.08219967,-0.17930984,-0.063595496,0.090810746,-0.06824588,0.0519749,0.018012317,-0.005835938,-0.023840599,0.0044698226,0.050769046,0.07054052,0.04608314,0.013581735,-0.033098806,0.020776583,-0.028363653,-0.006320364,0.029775256,-0.025796745,-0.032262947,-0.025397222,-0.06385178,0.0627657,0.07838207,-0.030126868,-0.018158719,-0.016070182,0.022442557,0.039181754,-0.030164877,-0.043459587,-0.0006082576,-0.05281568,-0.008749531,0.030675987,0.012652026,0.0019253455,-0.021526001,0.039834745,0.00844465,0.022955392,0.0026246987,0.053364936,0.0029912456,0.032644197,0.0034269558,0.10266945,-0.09925029,-0.021506822,0.031697508,0.04758409,0.01456493,0.08744729,0.05306573,-0.017052444,-0.008061911,-0.021651413,0.008352506,0.07624251,0.010749682,-0.029127775,0.07906499,0.060554627,-0.027611675,-0.016999329,0.039121866,0.03201146,-0.050445966,0.023471609,0.03093963,-0.052173898,0.028120406,-0.015664212,0.017656177,-0.008898131,-0.051788867,-0.026381632,0.04936065,0.013551727,-0.031548068,0.08478349,0.00235038