068ef2ed-d3bc-4237-be42-31c780ac3d71	6eea5a56-6837-41a7-89e7-130258343061	0	# Feature Idea: Semantic Wormholes\n\n**Connections that *shouldn't* exist but do.**\n\n---\n\n## The Insight\n\nOften the most valuable links between notes arise not from shared content but from shared **structural patterns**.  \nTwo seemingly unrelated domains—sourdough bread fermentation and software deployment pipelines—exhibit the same underlying workflow:\n\n- **Waiting for processes to complete**  \n- **Sensitivity to temperature / environment**  \n- **Determining readiness**  \n- **Iterative refinement over time**\n\nThese common patterns suggest that a richer linking strategy should look beyond semantic similarity and capture *process* and *temporal* structure.\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Strategy\n\n1. **Extract abstract patterns**  \n   - **Process flows**: e.g., `A → B → C`  \n   - **Conditional logic**: e.g., `if X then Y`  \n   - **Temporal patterns**: e.g., `wait`, `check`, `proceed`\n\n2. **Create pattern-based linkages**  \n   - Store each note with its extracted pattern metadata.  \n	[0.0062490893,0.05153771,-0.18320277,-0.06445876,0.0605977,-0.032729063,0.02025354,0.016815426,-0.02715468,-0.09496094,-0.002042409,0.0057579163,0.058348585,0.06688393,-0.0323922,-0.019476064,0.009421654,-0.0049871337,0.0017782234,0.059313703,-0.027614158,0.0072254897,0.039069537,-0.033676058,0.06008947,0.025816565,-0.018533804,-0.04389832,-0.04361089,-0.020166237,0.060188502,-0.05783769,-0.0288486,-0.049761266,-0.059504874,-0.061008725,-0.0013337277,0.0069072717,-0.009382199,0.029339235,0.028695304,0.06180641,-0.012703027,-0.04133779,0.025175214,0.030691098,0.015413847,0.030829843,0.04876839,-0.09489473,0.028099231,0.019803176,0.029228475,0.0045600277,0.08456861,0.051739078,0.07450591,0.049232405,-0.005835579,-0.037969876,0.025917381,0.084863156,-0.02983679,0.11301114,0.012150816,-0.015728058,-0.051952872,0.03206645,0.027374744,-0.028257728,0.042578544,-0.014539051,-0.014793293,0.037368644,-0.