848d7f93-0983-4641-ab76-3b3611631d6e	6f546182-c5ad-44aa-af54-7516b6f52596	0	# Feature Idea: **Note DNA**\n\n> Every note carries a genetic fingerprint that records *where* it came from and *why* it was created.\n\n---\n\n## 1. Concept\n\nWhen a user writes a new note the system automatically records its **lineage**:\n\n| Element | What to capture | Why it matters |\n|---------|-----------------|----------------|\n| **Source notes** | Notes that were open or referenced while writing | Shows knowledge dependencies |\n| **Search query** | The search string that led the user to the source | Helps trace the problem‑solving path |\n| **Context** | Time of day, device, or activity (e.g., “creative morning” vs. “analysis after lunch”) | Provides insight into personal productivity rhythms |\n\nThese data points form a **DNA trace** – a provenance chain that can be visualized like a family tree.\n\n---\n\n## 2. Why It Matters\n\n| Benefit | Description | Example |\n|---------|-------------|---------|\n	[0.055052597,0.03711169,-0.18574026,-0.03400335,0.06821731,-0.02924898,0.033199187,-0.007120605,-0.0049763145,-0.057903472,-0.04280136,0.039543297,0.09667605,0.066468135,0.003321543,-0.048206832,0.022439783,-0.019315572,0.01921506,0.062740475,-0.0010255198,-0.00023941304,-0.06901625,0.025785176,0.06313345,0.008812681,-0.00817393,-0.028104769,-0.010627688,-0.008360909,0.073037736,-0.023251746,-0.035589755,0.011025841,-0.07036992,-0.025217224,0.010132681,-0.008527988,0.027782504,0.06567723,0.046479486,0.037124697,-0.02709623,-0.04976396,0.025554273,0.030853169,0.014789061,0.010752563,0.074798815,-0.050879523,-0.003636841,0.005543731,0.015287634,0.008696868,0.08341408,0.063804835,0.0112917675,-0.031726368,0.008186118,-0.025578331,0.08783218,0.07775249,-0.051074985,0.10420047,0.042493884,-0.061685618,0.020104779,0.03828766,0.0121470755,-0.0094947,0.058681678,-0.04772048,-0.0064298436,0.016887307,0.0121348975,0.0052986373,-0.009718721,0.024004545,0.028820267,0.049157877,0.021204142,