226842df-5cbe-49d4-84c3-dd931fee5015	6f546182-c5ad-44aa-af54-7516b6f52596	3	| **Temporal Note Decay** | While DNA tracks lineage, decay assigns a *half‑life* to each note; combining them can surface aging insights (e.g., a lineage that was hot in 2024 but decayed in 2026). |\n\nThese features can be layered: a note’s DNA informs its decay schedule, and wormholes highlight lineage edges that should be preserved despite aging.\n\n---\n\n## 6. Broader Context\n\n- **Knowledge Graphs**: Note DNA essentially creates a lightweight, user‑centric graph that can be exported to a full knowledge graph for semantic search.\n- **Digital Archaeology**: The lineage provides a historical trail, enabling researchers to study the evolution of ideas within an organization.\n- **Personal Productivity**: By visualizing how thoughts emerge, users gain a meta‑cognitive tool to refine their workflows.\n\n---\n\n## 7. Takeaway\n\n	[0.034165185,0.023945367,-0.19967838,-0.06782938,0.06545463,-0.047915652,0.039369747,-0.0013105534,0.013808349,-0.058496792,-0.004351164,0.045261346,0.08370817,0.083499335,0.016528709,-0.058384907,0.0043115625,-0.016118854,0.04624923,0.06782145,0.01781189,-0.0069005154,-0.026717333,-0.004699643,0.04181532,0.070052445,-0.014619059,-0.0076756,-0.017845105,0.02456088,0.082854696,-0.0024297016,-0.038419053,0.03108516,-0.026419332,-0.025294574,0.040859148,0.0049602417,0.05007608,0.03668153,0.062165752,0.03718297,0.01268467,-0.01814308,0.050667543,0.008743708,0.01022944,-0.037060633,0.09733832,-0.09056295,0.012476665,0.05592345,0.040586874,0.025532587,0.020609349,0.038865138,-0.010002164,0.004930696,-0.008746305,-0.08477429,0.040901583,0.026612023,-0.009342391,0.06877711,0.04286289,-0.04563752,-0.016114775,0.008002355,-0.0022196807,-0.05850639,0.061736595,-0.03588747,0.002727468,0.03358553,-0.005992911,0.030794684,-0.0052771084,0.0018773896,0.007885349,0.010122633,0.002105656,-0.00074690586,0.029631998,0.028606143,0.08732946,-0.011610088,-0.043182515,-0.024990626,-0.042