82059ad0-f539-4698-94e9-60b579e5eb44	19e66f4d-a4f6-4d6e-9e26-7351abef625d	0	# Test Bulk 1\n\n- **# Test Bulk 1**  \n  *Created via bulk endpoint*\n\n## Test Bulk 2\n\n> Test **Bulk 2** was created through the **bulk endpoint**.  \n> This illustrates how a single API call can submit many records at once.\n\n---\n\n## Key Concepts\n\n| Concept | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Bulk Endpoint** | Allows a single API call to submit multiple records, reducing network round‑trips. |\n| **REST vs. GraphQL – Endpoint Design** | REST typically uses multiple distinct endpoints; GraphQL consolidates operations into one schema endpoint. |\n| **Caching Layer** | Stores frequently accessed data to improve response times. Evaluate **Valkey** as a Redis alternative for lower latency and advanced persistence. |\n\n---\n\n## Contextual Insights\n\n- **Efficiency of Bulk Calls** – By aggregating record submissions, bulk endpoints can dramatically improve throughput, especially under high‑volume conditions.\n	[0.004186456,0.083140254,-0.18341193,-0.057832852,0.086049564,-0.09207263,0.046776384,0.024661317,-0.038828693,0.006537973,-0.02476757,0.0016396982,0.058712408,0.0111388,-0.0035282199,-0.07440696,-0.032373503,-0.08654665,-0.017776487,0.041376334,-0.021005059,-0.012733278,0.007177689,-0.023150267,0.015202523,0.06946032,0.022880478,-0.01112526,-0.03844695,0.0021457474,0.026210684,-0.047528375,0.017909369,0.007926845,-0.07741821,-0.03660825,-0.012841248,-0.041059747,0.024265558,-0.020662013,0.029948995,-0.014545096,-0.0078077754,-0.049216583,0.013517971,-0.015832286,0.052998606,0.02195673,0.06171853,-0.07556695,-0.0054956037,-0.016014043,-0.030152041,-0.010583425,0.025581487,0.04139685,-0.038695343,0.065377444,0.026571456,-0.016721494,0.04819385,0.016165506,-0.037391827,0.0742274,0.062247057,0.011753794,-0.0072167856,-0.00047873025,0.03412939,-0.058324806,0.023525726,0.014291505,0.0071898005,-0.021586325,0.03298443,0.054697443,-0.0073565636,-0.027376851,-0.019970149,0.04