24bd1f88-794c-407b-974a-762d7054942a	b9e48d84-9081-4267-acd8-32a3d5cbe2cf	# MATRIC Platform Overview\n\n**MATRIC** = Managed Automation, Transformation, Reporting, Intelligence & Control\n\nA comprehensive AI orchestration and automation platform for enterprise workflow management.\n\n## Repository Structure\n\n| Repository | Description | Tech Stack |\n|------------|-------------|------------|\n| `matric` | Monorepo orchestrator with git submodules | Docker Compose, Make |\n| `matric-platform` | Core business logic, workflow engine, API services | Node.js/TypeScript, pnpm |\n| `matric-web` | Web application frontend | React/TypeScript |\n| `matric-intelligence` | AI/ML services | Python |\n| `matric-memory` | AI-enhanced note storage with semantic search | Rust, PostgreSQL/pgvector |\n| `matric-auth` | Authentication & secrets management | Keycloak, HashiCorp Vault |\n| `matric-infra` | Infrastructure as Code | Terraform |\n| `matric-sdk-js` | JavaScript SDK | TypeScript |\n| `matric-cli` | CLI tooling (11 open issues) | - |\n| `matric-fleet` | Fleet management | - |\n\n## Platform Packages (@matric/*)\n\n- `@matric/core` - Workflow engine and state machine\n- `@matric/cms` - Content management and versioning\n- `@matric/runtime` - Execution environments\n- `@matric/api` - API gateway and GraphQL endpoints\n- `@matric/types` - Shared TypeScript types\n- `@matric/common` - Shared utilities\n\n## Core Services (Docker)\n\n| Service | Port | Purpose |\n|---------|------|---------|\n| PostgreSQL | 5432 | Primary database |\n| MongoDB | 27017 | Document store (authenticated) |\n| Redis | 6379 | Caching and sessions |\n| Hasura | 8080 | GraphQL engine |\n| Keycloak | 8081/8443 | OIDC authentication |\n| Vault | 8200 | Secrets management |\n| MailPit | 1025/8025 | Email testing |\n| Grafana | 3000 | Monitoring dashboards |\n| Prometheus | 9090 | Metrics collection |\n\n## matric-memory Architecture (Rust)\n\nThe memory system is a Rust library with these crates:\n\n- `matric-core` - Core traits, types, error handling\n- `matric-db` - PostgreSQL + pgvector database layer\n- `matric-search` - Hybrid search (FTS + semantic + RRF fusion)\n- `matric-inference` - LLM inference abstraction (Ollama)\n- `matric-jobs` - Background job queue and processing\n- `matric-api` - HTTP REST API with OpenAPI/Swagger\n\n**Search Modes:**\n- Hybrid (default) - Combines FTS + semantic with RRF ranking\n- FTS only - Full-text search\n- Semantic only - Vector similarity search\n\n**Production URL:** https://memory.integrolabs.net\n\n## Authentication Architecture\n\n- **Keycloak**: OpenID Connect identity provider\n- **Vault**: JWT-based service authentication with role-based policies\n- **Multi-tenant**: User and tenant-scoped access control\n\n**Service Roles:**\n- `matric-service` - Standard service auth (1h TTL)\n- `matric-admin-service` - Admin operations (1h TTL)\n- `matric-monitor-service` - Read-only monitoring (30m TTL)\n\n## Development Commands\n\n```bash\n# Bootstrap entire platform\n./bootstrap.sh\n\n# Service management\nmake start|stop|restart|health|logs\n\n# HTTPS setup (local dev)\nmake setup-https\nmake check-certs\n\n# Database\nmake db-setup\n\n# Development\nmake dev|test|build|lint\n```\n\n## Current Status\n\n- Foundation stabilization phase (as of August 2025)\n- matric-cli has 11 open issues\n- matric-memory has 48 open issues (actively developed)	\N	2026-01-12 09:23:01.265434-05	\N	\N
32d10216-f6dc-4a74-a800-5e9ecae82cf0	b9e48d84-9081-4267-acd8-32a3d5cbe2cf	# MATRIC Platform Overview\n\n**MATRIC** = Managed Automation, Transformation, Reporting, Intelligence & Control  \nA comprehensive AI‑orchestration and automation platform for enterprise workflow management.\n\n## Repository Structure\n\n| Repository           | Description                                   | Tech Stack                                 |\n|----------------------|-----------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------|\n| `matric`             | Monorepo orchestrator with git submodules     | Docker Compose, Make                       |\n| `matric-platform`    | Core business logic, workflow engine, API services | Node.js/TypeScript, pnpm                  |\n| `matric-web`         | Web application frontend                      | React/TypeScript                           |\n| `matric-intelligence`| AI/ML services                                | Python                                     |\n| `matric-memory`      | AI‑enhanced note storage with semantic search | Rust, PostgreSQL/pgvector                  |\n| `matric-auth`        | Authentication & secrets management           | Keycloak, HashiCorp Vault                  |\n| `matric-infra`       | Infrastructure as Code                        | Terraform                                  |\n| `matric-sdk-js`      | JavaScript SDK                                | TypeScript                                 |\n| `matric-cli`         | CLI tooling (11 open issues)                  | –                                          |\n| `matric-fleet`       | Fleet management                              | –                                          |\n\n## Platform Packages (`@matric/*`)\n\n- `@matric/core` – Workflow engine and state machine  \n- `@matric/cms` – Content management and versioning  \n- `@matric/runtime` – Execution environments  \n- `@matric/api` – API gateway and GraphQL endpoints  \n- `@matric/types` – Shared TypeScript types  \n- `@matric/common` – Shared utilities  \n\n## Core Services (Docker)\n\n| Service     | Port(s) | Purpose                           |\n|-------------|---------|-----------------------------------|\n| PostgreSQL  | 5432    | Primary relational database       |\n| MongoDB     | 27017   | Document store (authenticated)   |\n| Redis       | 6379    | Caching and session store         |\n| Hasura      | 8080    | GraphQL engine                    |\n| Keycloak    | 8081/8443 | OIDC authentication              |\n| Vault       | 8200    | Secrets management                |\n| MailPit     | 1025/8025 | Email testing                    |\n| Grafana     | 3000    | Monitoring dashboards             |\n| Prometheus  | 9090    | Metrics collection                |\n\n## `matric-memory` Architecture (Rust)\n\nThe memory system is a Rust library composed of the following crates:\n\n- `matric-core` – Core traits, types, error handling  \n- `matric-db` – PostgreSQL + pgvector data layer  \n- `matric-search` – Hybrid search (FTS + semantic + RRF fusion)  \n- `matric-inference` – LLM inference abstraction (Ollama)  \n- `matric-jobs` – Background job queue and processing  \n- `matric-api` – HTTP REST API with OpenAPI/Swagger  \n\n### Search Modes\n\n| Mode            | Description                                       |\n|-----------------|---------------------------------------------------|\n| Hybrid (default) | Combines FTS + semantic vectors, ranked with RRF |\n| FTS only        | Pure full‑text search                              |\n| Semantic only   | Vector similarity search                           |\n\n**Production URL:** <https://memory.integrolabs.net>\n\n## Authentication Architecture\n\n- **Keycloak** – OpenID Connect identity provider  \n- **Vault** – JWT‑based service authentication with role‑based policies  \n- **Multi‑tenant** – User and tenant‑scoped access control  \n\n### Service Roles\n\n| Role                     | Description                          | TTL |\n|--------------------------|--------------------------------------|-----|\n| `matric-service`         | Standard service authentication      | 1 h |\n| `matric-admin-service`   | Administrative operations            | 1 h |\n| `matric-monitor-service` | Read‑only monitoring                 | 30 m |\n\n## Development Commands\n\n```bash\n# Bootstrap the entire platform\n./bootstrap.sh\n\n# Service management\nmake start|stop|restart|health|logs\n\n# HTTPS setup (local dev)\nmake setup-https\nmake check-certs\n\n# Database\nmake db-setup\n\n# Development tasks\nmake dev   # run dev servers\nmake test  # run tests\nmake build # build artifacts\nmake lint  # lint code\n```\n\n## Current Status\n\n- Foundation stabilization phase (as of August 2025)  \n- `matric-cli` has 11 open issues  \n- `matric-memory` has 48 open issues (actively developed)	AI-enhanced revision	2026-01-12 09:23:08.439244-05	\N	\N
